{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.840", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.360", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.280", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Zivilrecht ist die Revision beim Bundesgerichtshof m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn das Berufungsgericht im Urteil die Revision ausdr\u00fccklich zul\u00e4sst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens unabh\u00e4ngig vom Beschwerdewert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.800", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wird die Revision nicht zugelassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so kann gleichwohl eine Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde erhoben werden mit der M\u00f6glichkeit des Zugangs zum Bundesgerichtshof, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn der Berufungsstreitwert 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro \u00fcbersteigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute geht es um die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir die Wertgrenze f\u00fcr die Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro f\u00fcr die n\u00e4chsten eineinhalb Jahre fortschreiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich meine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.040", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist richtig und geboten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir diese Entscheidung treffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was w\u00fcrde passieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir die M\u00f6glichkeit einer Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde ab einer H\u00f6he des Streitwerts von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro nicht verl\u00e4ngern w\u00fcrden? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Belastung an den Zivilsenaten des Bundesgerichtshofs w\u00fcrde zunehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bereits jetzt sind die Verfahren vor den Zivilsenaten des Bundesgerichtshofs in der Mehrzahl sogenannte Nichtzulassungsbeschwerden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.440", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der Beibehaltung dieser Wertgrenze schneiden wir nicht das Recht des Revisionsf\u00fchrers ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz im Gegenteil: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ein Verfahren von rechtlich gro\u00dfer Bedeutung ist und wenn erkennbar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieses Verfahren eine Relevanz hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.560", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann wird das erkennende Gericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Landgericht oder das Oberlandesgericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.560", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohnehin die Revision zulassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.400", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens unabh\u00e4ngig vom Streitwert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber man darf nicht vergessen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in Deutschland den vollumf\u00e4nglichen Rechtsschutz nicht nur dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.200", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn jedes Verfahren bis zum BGH geht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss faktisch nicht die drei Instanzen aussch\u00f6pfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um zu seinem Recht zu kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.080", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in Deutschland eine exzellente Landschaft im Bereich der Oberlandesgerichte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Oberlandesgerichte haben Spezialkammern mit sehr spezialisierten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "guten Richtern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die einen ordentlichen Job machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.240", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Rechtsweggarantie des Grundgesetzes ist auf alle F\u00e4lle gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.680", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn jemand seine Rechtsstreitigkeit beim Landesgericht und dann beim Oberlandesgericht vorbringen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.840", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Bundesgerichtshof in wesentlichen Fragen des Versicherungsrechts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "des Mietrechts und des Bankenrechts grunds\u00e4tzliche Entscheidungen treffen muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.040", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf sollte sich der Bundesgerichtshof konzentrieren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.800", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es w\u00e4re falsch und w\u00fcrde dem Charakter eines obersten Bundesgerichtes nicht gerecht werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.080", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir den Bundesgerichtshof mit noch mehr Nichtzulassungsbeschwerden \u00fcberlasten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl es eine umfassende Rechtsschutzm\u00f6glichkeit bereits auf der Ebene des Landgerichts und des Oberlandesgerichts gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.440", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen uns bei diesem Thema klug verhalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir d\u00fcrfen die Architektur der Zivilrechtspflege nicht generell infrage stellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.520", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.480", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir m\u00fcssen uns \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.640", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir die permanente Fortschreibung der Wertgrenze von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro nicht generell regeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.480", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen dar\u00fcber diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir den Wert von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der \u00fcbrigens aus dem Jahr\u00a02001 stammt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.040", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht anheben oder indexieren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das gilt auch f\u00fcr andere Wertgrenzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber insgesamt sollten wir durch eine \u00c4nderung des Systems nicht grunds\u00e4tzlich das infrage stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.360", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in Deutschland gut funktioniert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich die Zivilrechtspflege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.480", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind aufgerufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alles zu tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.280", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf Ebene des Bundes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch auf Ebene der L\u00e4nder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.000", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um diese funktionierende Zivilrechtspflege weiterhin zu unterst\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch mehr Stellen bei der Justiz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.960", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch in den Gesch\u00e4ftsstellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.440", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch durch eine kluge Strategie zur weiteren Digitalisierung der Justiz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.680", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Digitalisierung von Akten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die E-Akte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.560", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betrifft \u00fcbrigens auch das Anwaltspostfach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich meine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.520", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sollte bald geregelt sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.640", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil nur indem man schnell an Akten kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen die Verfahren beschleunigt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist der wichtigste Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um im Zivilrechtsbereich nachhaltig eine gute L\u00f6sung f\u00fcr diejenigen hinzubekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.840", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Recht suchen und bei uns auch ihr Recht bekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.720", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Sinne bitte ich um Zustimmung zu diesem Gesetzentwurf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.320", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die n\u00e4chste Rednerin ist f\u00fcr die FDP-Fraktion die Kollegin Katrin Helling-Plahr."
   ]
  }
 ]
}